definition: every kind of/all kinds of/various kinds

sentences.english: Sales of a variety of consumer-related products are gaining steadily.
sentences.chinese: 各種消費食品的銷售在穩步上升。

sentences.english: They are strictly vegetarian and eat all manner of deep fried food.
sentences.chinese: 他們是嚴格的食素者，喫各種各樣的油炸食品。

sentences.english: The audiences enjoyed the moon and the lanterns while solving the riddles in a relaxed way.
sentences.chinese: 中秋夜人們將謎條張貼在各種花燈之上，賞月猜謎。

sentences.english: One cannot overlook his uncanny ability to navigate the many political intrigues and maneuverings.
sentences.chinese: 沒人能忽略他平息各種政治陰謀詭計的稟賦。

sentences.english: He outshone his fellow pupils in every skill.
sentences.chinese: 他在各種技能上都比他的同學更出色。

sentences.english: In this paper, the newest developing of plastic optical fiber is reviewed for various communication.
sentences.chinese: 本文綜述了各種通信用塑料光纖研究的最新進展。

sentences.english: The magnetic coupling also can be used in autoclaves and mixers .
sentences.chinese: 磁力傳動器亦可用於各種高壓容器及攪拌釜上。

sentences.english: He has a better eye for similarities among cultures than for diversities.
sentences.chinese: 他看各種文化之間的相似點比看其相異點更爲透徹。

sentences.english: Wolter products are used both in general building services applications as well as various industrial areas.
sentences.chinese: 華徳產品一般是用在建築服務和各種工業領域。

sentences.english: Recommended for all non-sensitive skin types.
sentences.chinese: 各種皮膚，敏感皮膚不建議使用。

sentences.english: Neil: There's also the world's largest collection of TVs.
sentences.chinese: 這裏還有世界收藏量最廣最大的各種電視機。

sentences.english: All kinds of medicine to eat, especially those containing hormone medicine.
sentences.chinese: 各種藥都要少喫，特別是一些含有激素的藥。

sentences.chinese: 分析影響航天器長期伴隨飛行的各種因素。

sentences.english: This article aims to analyze various processing methods for groundwater excavation of the foundation ditch in earthwork construction.
sentences.chinese: 分析土方工程施工中基坑開挖地下水的各種處理辦法。

sentences.english: A bowl-shaped desert island inhabited by a variety of monsters.
sentences.chinese: 狹長的沙漠島，息居着各種各樣的怪獸。

sentences.english: It is a neighborhood beset by all the usual inner-city problems.
sentences.chinese: 這是個爲各種內城常見問題所困擾的社區。
